'''AUDIO ENTRY FILE -- TRANSCRIPTED FOR READING'''

[For the security of the recorders, the names of the individuals inside of '''AUDIO_ENTRY_FILE_REP89''' will not be listed. Instead, unique individuals will be given their own subject number.

'''Subject #1:''' Is this thing on? [Pauses] Yeah it's on, there's a red dot right there. Okay, uh. Hi. I'm '''[EXPUNGED]''' and right now we're inside of Level '''[EXPUNGED]'''.  We're hearing this really high pitched ringing sound--well I say we but it's really just me an [SUBJECT #2] hearing it. [SUBJECT #3] over there is as happy as can be. We've tried talking to him but he just smiles at us. When has there ever been anything to smile about here? [Pauses] Hold up, I wonder if this thing can hear it.

[Static ambience.]

'''Subject #1:''' Hopefully it got that.

'''Subject #2:''' Ugh, I'm about to ''rip my ears off.'' I'm tired of this ringing sound. We need to no-clip somewhere before I lose my ever loving mind.

'''Subject #1:''' Hang in there, man. We just got here, could be part of what this place does.

[A loud explosion is captured by the device, a clatter is heard. Subject #1 later reports the device was thrown by the explosion.]

[Distant.]

'''Subject #2:''' What the fuck! [Subject #3] just fucking blew up! Oh my God! [SUBJECT #1]!

'''Subject #1:''' I'm okay! I'm okay! Just a bit banged up! Give me a hand here, [SUBJECT #2]!

[Loud crash.]

'''Subject #2:''' Holy shit! That whole chunk of ceiling fell!

[Subject #3 Reportedly remanifest here.]

'''Subject #3:''' What the happened to ''you'', [SUBJECT #1]?

'''Subject #2:''' How the fuck! [Cuts off.] How are you alive!

'''Subject #3:''' What do you mean "how"? Breathing, eating, drinking. [Cut off by Subject #1]

'''Subject #1:''' No, you just blew up for fuck's sake! How are you alive!

'''Subject #2:''' What if he's a Skinstealer? Get the knife.

'''Subject #3:''' What? No, I'm not a Skinstealer! I was born on '''[EXPUNGED]''' and we were on Level 69 just an hour or so ago. Would a Skinstealer know ''that''?

'''Subject #1:''' Point proven. But, you ''exploded''. Did you not feel yourself getting ripped apart?

'''Subject #3:''' Did I really? I mean, it's a bit warm here. But, I mean did I really no shit ''explode''?

'''Subject #2:''' Yes! Do you not see the collapsed ceiling!

'''Subject #3:''' Are [Pauses] are you two needing almond water? We have some in the pack, you know.

'''Subject #2:''' No! We're not! Fuck's sake, he's gone mad.

'''Subject #1:''' Wait, where's the recorder? [Pauses] Oh there, it is. Still recording, thank God.

[Footsteps]

'''Subject #1:''' Let's get this thing to an outpost and see." [Cuts off]

[LOG ENDED] 
